OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FThree people have died in a suspected
OL,8,Foutbreak of hantavirus on a cruise
OL,9,Fship in the Atlantic Ocean, the World
OL,10,FHealth Organisation (WHO) has said.
OL,12,FWHO said on Wednesday, May 6, that
OL,13,Fthree cases of hantavirus infection
OL,14,Fhave been confirmed, with five
OL,15,Fadditional suspected cases.
OL,17,FAmong them are two Dutch nationals and
OL,18,Fone German who died of illnesses
OL,19,Flinked to the virus after boarding the
OL,20,FMV Hondius' cruise of the Antarctic
OL,21,Fand South Atlantic islands.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
