OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FThree people were evacuated from the
OL,8,Fship on Wednesday and were on their
OL,9,Fway to the Netherlands for urgent
OL,10,Fmedical treatment.
OL,12,FAmong them was a British doctor who
OL,13,Fwas in a serious condition but is now
OL,14,Fdescribed by health authorities as
OL,15,Fstable.
OL,17,FITV News explains what hantavirus is
OL,18,Fand how it spreads.
OL,20,FWhat is hantavirus?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
