OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FHantaviruses are a group of viruses
OL,8,Fthat are normally carried by rodents,
OL,9,Fsuch as rats, mice and voles.
OL,11,FThey are present throughout the world
OL,12,Fand can cause a range of diseases in
OL,13,Fhumans ranging from mild, flu-like
OL,14,Fillness to severe respiratory illness
OL,15,For haemorrhagic disease with kidney
OL,16,Fissues.
OL,18,FHow does it spread?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
