OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FHantavirus is mainly spread by contact
OL,8,Fwith rodents or their urine, saliva or
OL,9,Fdroppings, particularly when the
OL,10,Fmaterial is disturbed and becomes
OL,11,Fairborne, posing risk of inhalation.
OL,13,FPeople are typically exposed to
OL,14,Fhantavirus around their homes, cabins
OL,15,For sheds, especially when cleaning out
OL,16,Fenclosed spaces with little
OL,17,Fventilation or exploring areas where
OL,18,Fthere are mouse droppings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
