OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FWHO says that while it rarely happens,
OL,8,Fhantaviruses can also spread directly
OL,9,Fbetween people, and has suggested that
OL,10,Fthis may have been the case on board
OL,11,Fthe MV Hondius.
OL,13,FOfficials from the United Nations
OL,14,Fhealth body confirmed that the Andes
OL,15,Fstrain of the virus is spreading.
OL,17,FThe strain, which is prevalent in
OL,18,FSouth America and has been shown to
OL,19,Fspread between humans, although this
OL,20,Fmethod of transmission is still rare
OL,21,Foverall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
