OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,F"The risk to the general public is
OL,8,Flow," WHO's head of epidemic and
OL,9,Fpandemic preparedness and prevention,
OL,10,FDr Maria Van Kerkhove, told a news
OL,11,Fconference in Geneva.
OL,13,F"This is not a virus that spreads like
OL,14,Fflu or like Covid... It's quite
OL,15,Fdifferent."
OL,17,FWhat are the symptoms?
OL,19,FSymptoms can include:
