OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FSymptoms of hantavirus pulmonary
OL,8,Fsyndrome usually show between one to
OL,9,Feight weeks after contact with an
OL,10,Finfected rodent. As the infection
OL,11,Fprogresses, patients might experience
OL,12,Ftightness in the chest, as the lungs
OL,13,Ffill with fluid.
