OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FAn infection can rapidly progress and
OL,8,Fbecome life-threatening.
OL,10,FThe disease gained attention last year
OL,11,Fafter late actor Gene Hackman's wife,
OL,12,FBetsy Arakawa, died from a hantavirus
OL,13,Finfection in New Mexico.
OL,15,FWhat is the cure?
OL,17,FThere is no specific treatment or
OL,18,Fcure, but early medical attention can
OL,19,Fincrease the chance of survival.
OL,21,FHow can you avoid hantavirus?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
