OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1778080262
OL,3,CWhat is hantavirus, the illness
OL,4,Csuspected to have killed three on a
OL,5,Ccruise ship?
OL,7,FThe best way to avoid the germ is to
OL,8,Fminimise contact with rodents and
OL,9,Ftheir droppings, and using protective
OL,10,Fgloves and a bleach solution for
OL,11,Fcleaning up rodent droppings.
OL,13,FPublic health experts caution against
OL,14,Fsweeping or vacuuming which can cause
OL,15,Fvirus to get into the air.
